title: Sinead O'Connor - I Do Not Want... Limited Ed.  FLAC
description:
Sinead O'Connor - I Do Not Want What I Haven't Got - Limited Edition 2009

I've previously uploaded the original release of this but when I 
saw there was a limited edition, I had to have it.  This is for 
the flac heads. The Bonus Disc is great and the live version of
Troy is FREAKIN' AWESOME!!!

The disc was ripped to flac using EAC.  The upload includes 
cue sheet, log file, playlist and artwork.  Enjoy.
